{"id":581248,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【立此存照】胡锡进新浪微博再度广告：求推特/","date":"2018-03-21T07:04:18Z","modified":"2018-03-21T07:04:18Z","title":"【立此存照】胡锡进新浪微博再度广告：求推特“关注”","content":"<p>3月21日，《环球时报》总编辑胡锡进再度在新浪微博提及自己的推特账号 @HuXijin_huanqiu ，证明其真实性，并且提到自己近期被诸多账号假冒。3月4日，胡锡进在新浪微博宣布自己开通了推特账号，截至目前，胡锡进发推36条，收获关注者1.52W，每一条消息下都有大量的推友回pi复ping。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-581256\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进2.jpg 728w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进2-300x233.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>@胡锡进：老胡两周前开了个中文推特账号，经常有假冒者编排老胡在推特上说了什么什么。大家注意，只有下面这个中文推特账号是老胡的，它的跟众量大约1.5万。假老胡账号的跟众量都很少。还望朋友们力挺老胡。老胡这条又要关评论，请谅。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/7697cf01ly1fpkd9gcizmj20qo1bfakq.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-581250\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/7697cf01ly1fpkd9gcizmj20qo1bfakq.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/7697cf01ly1fpkd9gcizmj20qo1bfakq.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/7697cf01ly1fpkd9gcizmj20qo1bfakq-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/7697cf01ly1fpkd9gcizmj20qo1bfakq-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_581255\" style=\"width: 450px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-581255\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进.jpg 393w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进-295x300.jpg 295w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/胡锡进-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">推特搜索胡锡进，可以看到很多名称相似账号。</p></div>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E3%80%90%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%91%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E8%83%A1%E9%94%A1%E8%BF%9B%EF%BC%9A%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E7%BF%BB%E5%A2%99%E4%B8%8A%E6%8E%A8%E6%9D%A5%E8%AE%B2/\">【网络民议】环球胡锡进：欢迎大家推特上来讲真话</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[22838,14865,9000,26601,23901,8604,8859,15525,9212,20282]}